  drawer.innerHTML=`<div class="nav38-backdrop" data-close="1"></div><section class="nav38-panel" role="dialog" aria-modal="true" aria-label="GoalOS site navigation"><div class="nav38-head"><div><div class="nav38-kicker">Complete public navigation</div><h2>Choose the proof path.</h2><p>Every page remains available. The menu groups the site by user intent and keeps public pages default-deny.</p></div><button class="nav38-close" type="button" data-close="1">Close</button></div><div class="nav38-search"><input type="search" aria-label="Search GoalOS pages" placeholder="Search proof, evidence, settlement, legal, router…"><a href="${base}experience-hub.html">Experience Hub</a></div><div class="nav38-journeys"></div><div class="nav38-groups"></div></section>`;
